117
00:04:40,000 --> 00:04:41,160
Don't blame her.

118
00:04:41,680 --> 00:04:42,319
Bring it here.

119
00:04:51,759 --> 00:04:52,279
Your Highness.

120
00:04:58,000 --> 00:04:58,839
