133
00:05:23,959 --> 00:05:25,279
Your mental state is good.

134
00:05:25,800 --> 00:05:27,360
Keep your weight and blood sugar stable.

135
00:05:27,560 --> 00:05:29,720
Stop eating these sugary pastries.

136
