144
00:06:15,480 --> 00:06:16,240
Ziheng.

145
00:06:16,399 --> 00:06:17,319
Why are you here?

146
00:06:17,639 --> 00:06:19,680
Wei Ziheng, that jinxed prince.

147
00:06:20,279 --> 00:06:21,680
Even if you are a prince,

148
00:06:21,680 --> 00:06:23,279
