150
00:06:25,680 --> 00:06:26,720
Me?

151
00:06:26,720 --> 00:06:28,120
Harm your mother?

152
00:06:29,199 --> 00:06:29,759
Mother.

153
00:06:29,920 --> 00:06:32,800
