185
00:07:47,319 --> 00:07:47,800
Mother.

186
00:07:47,959 --> 00:07:48,920
I'll handle everything properly.

187
00:07:49,439 --> 00:07:50,279
Please rest well.

188
00:08:01,759 --> 00:08:02,519
